title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-24-2014 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-24-2014 MON....PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/24/14Monday, February 24, 2014 10:38 AM


Glenn talks about the future of technology with Google 
    as he preps to sit down with Google executive chairman Eric Schmidt 
      and Director of Google Ideas Jared Cohen. 

 Also, the guys take a moment to reflect on the cancellation of Piers Morgan's show on CNN.


  Plus, Heidi Huber of Ohians Against Common Core joins the show 
       to discuss what is happening with Common Core in America.
